Value.value: By the Nine Hells! You entered a temple of Ghaunadaur, the mad god of Slimes and Oozes. That creature down there must be some aspect of him. You notice that this must have been a temple to Lotlh one day. Her statues have been defaced and replaced by ... formless things.
The altar isn't part of the original furniture. When you look into the pool you see two big eyes staring back at you. Is this what they call "He who lurks in the deep"?
This is a crude altar. There seems to be some creepy pool behind it.
